&lt;p&gt;Famous House in the Povarskaya Street once became a gathering place for famous writers, artists, representatives of the cultural elite, and was visited by respected politicians. Now this is a famous place among the residents and guests of the capital. This is one of the best places for weddings, banquets, presentations!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stylistic features of the magnificent neo-Gothic interior of the mansion, which was built in the late 19th century, preserved to this day. Over the decades of its existence, the building served&nbsp;as a family nest for a famous noble family, Masonic lodge, overnight shelter for poor proletarians, writing office and restaurant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And now C.D.L. &ndash; is the restaurant visited daily by dozens of connoisseurs of traditional Russian cuisine in the author&amp;#8217;s performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every guest not only can enjoy the culinary masterpieces, but also to become a participant in cultural programs. They are held regularly at the restaurant. An indescribable atmosphere here is created by well-known domestic and foreign musicians. Ordinary residents and visitors, as well as recognizable politicians, businessmen and media persons come here to spend an evening in their company, dining to fascinating music.&lt;/p&gt;
